Set up game board
    Define board size
    Draw vertical line down middle of screen
    Draw 2 paddles, one on the left, one on the right, same size
    Draw ball in the middle

Set up scoreboard
    "Left" player score
    "Right" player score
    Function for incrementing score based on ball position

Set up controls
    "Left" player controls (W A S D)
    "Right" player controls (Up Down Left Right)

Ball movement
    Determine how to have the ball move based on how it hits the paddle

game board set up, ball physics, and controls will be in 'main.py', scoreboard in 'scoreboard.py',